n33: | AR-039-002-B | router | HealthChecker.Start/Stop | Health checker monitors backends and marks unavailable | 🔲 |\n34: \n35: ### router 模块 - 限流\n36: \n37: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n38: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n39: | AR-039-003-A | router | RateLimiter.Allow | Rate limiter allows requests under limit | 🔲 |\n40: | AR-039-003-B | router | RateLimiter.Allow | Rate limiter blocks requests over limit with 429 | 🔲 |\n41: | AR-039-003-C | router | RateLimiter.Allow | Rate limiter can be disabled | 🔲 |\n42: \n43: ### router 模块 - 认证\n44: \n45: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n46: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n47: | AR-039-004-A | router | Authenticator.Middleware | Authenticator validates token correctly | 🔲 |\n48: | AR-039-004-B | router | Authenticator.Middleware | Authenticator can be disabled | 🔲 |\n49: \n50: ### router 模块 - Session 管理\n51: \n52: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n53: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n54: | AR-039-005-A | router | SessionManager | Session manager creates session | 🔲 |\n55: | AR-039-005-B | router | SessionManager | Session cleanup removes expired sessions | 🔲 |\n56: | AR-039-005-C | router | SessionMiddleware | Session middleware attaches session to request | 🔲 |\n57: \n58: ### router 模块 - JWT 认证\n59: \n60: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n61: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n62: | AR-039-006-A | router | JWTManager.GenerateToken | JWT manager creates token with correct claims | 🔲 |\n63: | AR-039-006-B | router | JWTManager.ValidateToken | JWT manager validates valid/expired/invalid tokens | 🔲 |\n64: | AR-039-006-C | router | JWTMiddleware.Middleware | JWT middleware enforces authentication | 🔲 |\n65: \n66: ### router 模块 - 日志和指标\n67: \n68: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n69: |----|-----------|----------|-----------