n178: | store_valkey.go | store_valkey_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n179: | store_redis.go | store_redis_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n180: \n181: ### picod 模块\n182: \n183: | Source File | Test File | Status |\n184: |-------------|-----------|--------|\n185: | server.go | server_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n186: | execute.go | execute_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n187: | auth.go | auth_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n188: | files.go | files_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n189: | health.go | health_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n190: \n191: ---\n192: \n193: ## 验收标准\n194: \n195: - [ ] AC001: Router Config 初始化和默认值测试\n196: - [ ] AC002: Router 创建各种配置组合测试\n197: - [ ] AC003: BackendPool AddBackend, RemoveBackend, GetBackendForRequest 测试\n198: - [ ] AC004: HealthChecker Start, Stop, checkBackend 测试\n199: - [ ] AC005: RateLimiter Allow, Middleware 测试\n200: - [ ] AC006: Authenticator Middleware 启用/禁用状态测试\n201: - [ ] AC007: SessionManager Create, Get, Delete, Cleanup 测试\n202: - [ ] AC008: JWTManager GenerateToken, ValidateToken 测试\n203: - [ ] AC009: JWTMiddleware 各种配置测试\n204: - [ ] AC010: Logger Middleware 测试\n205: - [ ] AC011: Metrics IncBackendRequests, RecordRequestDuration, IncErrors 测试\n206: - [ ] AC012: Valkey store 连接模拟客户端测试\n207: - [ ] AC013: StoreSandbox 有效和无效输入测试\n208: - [ ] AC014: GetSandboxBySessionID 存在/不存在会话测试\n209: - [ ] AC015: UpdateSandbox 测试\n210: - [ ] AC016: DeleteSandboxBySessionID 测试\n211: - [ ] AC017: ListExpiredSandboxes 测试\n212: - [ ] AC018: ListInactiveSandboxes 测试\n213: - [ ] AC019: UpdateSessionLastActivity 测试\n214: - [ ] AC020: Close 测试\n215: - [ ] AC021: Server 创建有效和无效配置测试\n216: - [ ] AC022: setWorkspace 测试\n217: - [ ] AC023: sanitizePath 各种路径输入测试\n218: - [ ] AC024: AuthManager LoadPublicKeyFromEnv, ValidateToken 测试\n219: - [ ] AC025: auth middleware 公共/受保护路径测试\n220: - [ ] AC026: ExecuteHandler 有效命令、超时、无效工作目录测试\n221: - [ ] AC027: UploadFileHandler, ListFilesHandler, DownloadFileHandler 测试\n222: - [ ] AC028: HealthCheckHandler 测试\n223: - [ ] AC029: LoadRSAPublicKey 测试\n224: - [ ] AC030: router, store, picod 包的现有测试保持通过\n225: \n226: ---\n227: \n228: ## 依赖\n229: \n230: - Go 1.21+\n231: - `testing` package (stdlib)\n232: - `github.com/stretchr/testify` - 断言和 mock\n233: - `github.com/golang/mock` 或 `go generate` - mock 生成\n234: - `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` - Valkey 客户端\n235: \n236: ---\n237: \n238: ## 测试模式\n239: \n240: ### Mock 策略\n241: - 对依赖项使用接口 (Store, HTTP clients 等)\n242: - 使用 testify/mock 创建测试 mock\n243: - 对复杂模块使用 gomock 生成 mocks\n244: \n245: ### 测试文件命名\n246: - 遵循 Go 约定: `*_test.go`\n247: - 与被测代码保持在同一包中\n248: - 使用 `package router` (不是 `package router_test`)\n249: \n250: ### 表驱动测试\n251: - 对参数化场景使用表驱动测试\n252: - 示例模式:\n253: ```go\n254: tests := []struct {\n255:     name    string\n256:     input   string\n257:     want    string\n258:     wantErr bool\n259: }{...}\n260: ```\n261: \n262: ### 测试覆盖率目标\n263: - Router 模块: 70%+ 代码覆盖率\n264: - Store 模块: 80%+ 代码覆盖率\n265: - Picod 模块: 70%+ 代码覆盖率\n266: \n267: ---\n268: \n269: ## 参考\n270: \n271: - Router 模块: `pkg/router/`\n272: - Store 模块: `pkg/store/`\n273: - Picod 模块: `pkg/picod/`\n274: - 通用类型: `pkg/common/types/`\n275: - 基础规范 (client-go): `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n\n(End of file - total 275 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-039: Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod) - Delta Spec\n\n> **Module:** pkg\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** L\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing Go unit tests for three core modules:\n- **pkg/router**: HTTP routing, proxy, health checking, rate limiting, authentication, session management, JWT\n- **pkg/store**: Valkey/Redis-backed session and sandbox storage\n- **pkg/picod**: Pico execution server with command execution and file handling\n\n---\n\n## Test Scenarios\n\n### router 模块 - 初始化和配置","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775883379577,"end":1775883379592}}}}
